      "span_text": "Additionally, specific mAbs to the target proteins (VP72-ASFV and E2-CSFV) were used in parallel to the reference sera to determine analytical sensitivity. 18BG3 mAb a was used to determine the sensitivity for the ASF test line, following a previously described protocol, and the 18.4 mAb b was used for the CSF test line."
